<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yōng yǒu zhǔ 迦南91</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yōng yǒu zhǔ shén me dōu bù yào, yōng yǒu zhǔ yī qiè dōu gòu le,
 shuō shén me qīn rén dōu lí qì wǒ, shuō shén me zài fēng yǔ zhōng piāo yáo,
 wǒ de yǎn zhǐ yǎng wàng zhǔ, shēn zhī tā cóng bù diū qì wǒ,
 yī shēng suī shì làng jī hǎi jiǎo tiān yá, yōng yǒu zhǔ wǒ xīn jiù mǎn zú le.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>91</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>